Ecochlor | Ballast Water Treatment System























































12 Years at Sea
The Ecochlor® Ballast Water Treatment System: proven effective and reliable for over 12 years at sea. The rugged, scalable, modular system offers installation and operational advantages.
Get a quick overview of the system here →

 







                    Rugged, Modular System                  
Highly efficient system offers space, energy, and operational advantages over other ballast water treatment systems.








                    Proven ClO2 Technology                  
Chlorine dioxide (ClO2) has been used in water treatment and industrial applications for 70 years, and on ships for 12 years.








                    Install Case Studies                  
Take a look at our installation and feasibility case studies. The Ecochlor system is ideal for larger bulkers and tankers.








                    How It Works                  
Animated video shows how the system works to produce a biocide, as needed, to disinfect ballast water and meet or exceed existing regulations.






