ECOCHLOR INC        



ECOCHLOR INC


The Ecochlor BWTS uses a two-step process - filtration followed by disinfection with chlorine dioxide. The system's effectiveness is not impaired by variations in salinity, temperature, turbidity, organics, and vibration. Furthermore, the small size, low power and low maintenance make it ideally suited for installation on the world's largest ships. The Ecochlor BWTS has completed all testing for USCG Type Approval.




